Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.27,0:00:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把房间弄得光亮些
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.04,0:00:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后离我远一点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.13,0:00:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在对可惠队长  敬礼!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.59,0:00:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早怎么这么吵?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.64,0:00:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晨,太郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.96,0:00:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是可惠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.64,0:00:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她要外出
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.31,0:00:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在交代警备的事务
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.65,0:00:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊? 可惠要出门去吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.94,0:02:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\pos(350,390)}『可惠的锻炼』
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.78,0:02:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上山狩猎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对,每年这个时候我都会出去修练
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.47,0:02:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果只是平常的锻炼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.31,0:02:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会让自己的技术退步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.07,0:02:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大自然里面也可以锻炼身心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.40,0:02:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.11,0:02:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没那么棒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.52,0:02:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.77,0:02:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎大人也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.08,0:02:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对,就这么办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.89,0:02:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有守卫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.27,0:02:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不一定每次都可以保护
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.82,0:02:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了预防万一太郎大人也必须接受锻炼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.51,0:02:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请马上去做准备
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃? 啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.65,0:02:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请保重
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.30,0:02:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,, 啊!～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.33,0:03:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何? 太郎大人你来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这大自然的风景
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.59,0:03:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们该下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.90,0:03:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.42,0:03:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要做什么?!......
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.34,0:03:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先...先洁净身体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.08,0:03:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果身心无法合一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.03,0:03:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会输给瀑布的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.94,0:03:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身心合一...  身心合一...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是可惠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好象很镇定的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.56,0:03:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.77,0:03:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.05,0:04:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...你没事吧,太郎大人?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是流木或者是什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起,有我在你身边  却...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.45,0:04:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为从来没做过  所以没法做的好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.01,0:04:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎大人的腰力不够
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.03,0:04:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手腕和腰力要一致
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚步要站稳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腰部放低一点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后再用力拉绳子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.51,0:04:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个连贯动作要做的更加顺畅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.03,0:05:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我来作一次给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.54,0:05:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请仔细看着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.58,0:05:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样  这样!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.52,0:05:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(是栗子!)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起...我太激动了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.37,0:05:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.58,0:05:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腰部再用力些!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在拳头挥出去的瞬间用力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要像这样子,太郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.54,0:05:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎大人,不是这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.22,0:05:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里要用点腰力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.09,0:06:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惠,你的胸部...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的肩膀上面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸部  胸部  胸部...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.41,0:06:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎大人!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.22,0:06:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起,我太不小心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.78,0:06:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.64,0:06:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎大人请等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上准备晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.04,0:06:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近会有什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.25,0:06:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香鱼或者鳝鱼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些鱼都是很难钓的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.49,0:06:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们就不要用钓的那么麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.01,0:06:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个方法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.81,0:06:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到你会用这种方法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:07:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候和朋友都是这样抓鱼的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.89,0:07:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么做呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.13,0:07:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.20,0:07:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要对准大石头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.83,0:07:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用力的丢过去就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.97,0:07:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是引起突发的震动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让那些鱼昏过去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.63,0:07:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对,这么大就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.68,0:07:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到了吗,太郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.33,0:07:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎大人?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.62,0:07:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太...太郎大人!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.21,0:07:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我太兴奋了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.84,0:07:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.66,0:08:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何,和平时在庭园跑相比跑山路很累吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.73,0:08:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离目的地还很远
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.85,0:08:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.08,0:08:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.73,0:08:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是山野兔  好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.06,0:08:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦? 还有一只吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.37,0:09:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs50}救命啊!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.41,0:09:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎大人...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.43,0:09:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉,有我在你身边...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.19,0:09:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何? 还能跑吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.01,0:09:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.73,0:09:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这种精神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.95,0:09:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是想让太郎大人看这幅景色
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有一个姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.65,0:09:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个非常厉害  非常棒的一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.54,0:10:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我除了对她的敬仰  还有以她作为目标
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.94,0:10:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才会开始在这里进行修练的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.19,0:10:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这种修练辛苦的让人喘不过气来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过每次看到这夕阳   一切的辛苦都忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.77,0:10:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.70,0:10:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎大人  你做的很好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.74,0:10:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一天让你强壮了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.70,0:10:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.89,0:10:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在,太郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.37,0:10:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在休息之前先去流些汗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.78,0:10:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.06,0:10:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近有个天然温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.27,0:10:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这主意不错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.31,0:10:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服  真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.19,0:10:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这温泉真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.35,0:11:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温度刚刚好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.21,0:11:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何  伤口会痛吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.69,0:11:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.44,0:11:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.51,0:11:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.85,0:11:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办? 健康男人的生理现象...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.58,0:11:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?  怎么了,太郎大人?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.57,0:11:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你的样子很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.83,0:11:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.88,0:11:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么说...这是没办法的事...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先离开一下或许...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.63,0:11:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你在身心方面的修练还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.04,0:12:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎大人和可惠呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.50,0:12:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是去接他们吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.50,0:12:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是,听说他们好象还要再继续修练一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.56,0:12:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.95,0:12:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在太郎大人还没有得到健全的身心前...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.83,0:12:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想回家!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽这么说...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.46,0:12:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因都是可惠你啊～～!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.83,0:13:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我让主人受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.17,0:13:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我让主人遇到危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.48,0:13:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我让主人...思春了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.71,0:14:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太郎大人,好合身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.87,0:14:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第15话『依良的经验』
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.73,0:14:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回也要好好的听主人差遣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.34,0:14:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿上女装  做个女佣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.22,0:14:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依良的恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.93,0:14:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有她的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.42,0:14:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事暂时不谈
